1. BTC briefly broke through 86,000 USDT;
2. Ethereum spot ETF had a total net outflow of 41.8245 million USD yesterday, and continued net outflow for 7 days;
3. 5 whale addresses have transferred 3.54 million SOL to Coinbase in the past 12 hours;
4. Bitcoin returned to the top ten in the global asset market value ranking;
5. A contract trader opened a long position of 142 million USD BTC again in the early hours of this morning;
6. The White House will hold a cryptocurrency summit on March 7;
7. Tether issued 1 billion USDT on the TRON network this morning.
